Ugbad Abdi bụ onye America na-eme ejiji nlereanya

A mụrụ ya na Somalia ma zụlite ya n'ogige ndị gbara ọsọ ndụ Kenya na Des Moines, Iowa, ọ malitere dị ka onye na-emepụta ejiji Valentino haute, wee mepee ihe ngosi maka Marc Jacobs na Michael Kors na izu Ejiji nke New York
Ọ bụ onye nlereanya ejiji mbụ mere ngosi ejiji nlereanya nyena Fendi na Lanvin mgbe o yi hijab.
A mụrụ Abdi na Kismayo, Somalia

Ezinụlọ ya gbapụrụ n'ihi agha obodo Somalia, na mbụ gaa n'ogige ndị gbara ọsọ ndụ]] na Kenya, mgbe ahụ na 2009, mgbe Abdi dị afọ itoolu, ha agaa Des Moines, Iowa site n'enyemaka UNICEF. N'oge na-adịghị anya mgbe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị na Des Moines, e nyopụtara Abdi na Instagram. Ọ gara New York na nke mbụ ya iji zute ndị nnọchi anya ụlọ ọrụ, wee bịanye aka nye Next Management.

Abdi mere ihe ngosi izizi ya n'afọ 2018/2019 Valentino haute couture show. O meghere ihe ngosi New York Fashion Week maka Marc Jacobs na Michael Kors. Abdi agagharịwokwa na ihe ngosi maka Chanel, Miu Miu, Simone Rocha, Burberry, Fendi, Lanvin, Max Mara, na Dries van Noten. N'ọnwa Eprel nke afọ 2019, ọ pụtara na mbipụta British, American, na Arabic nke Vogue n'otu oge. A na-akpọ Abdi "otu n'ime ndị na-eme ihe ngosi nke ọdịda 2019". N'afọ 2022, ọ pụtara n'ihu Vogue France na onye Danish model Mona Tougaard.
Abdi bụ onye okpukpe Alakụba, ọ malitekwara iyi hijab mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na anọ
Ọ na-eyi ihe mkpuchi isi mgbe ọ na-eme ihe ngosi, na 2019 ọ ghọrọ ihe nlereanya mbụ nke Fendi na Lanvin na-eyi hijab. O nwere ụmụnne ise, abụọ n'ime ha amụrụ mgbe ezinụlọ ahụ kwagara United States
